        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "At this moment the King, who had been for some time busily writing in his note book, cackled out 'Silence!' and read out from his book, 'Rule Forty two.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
