        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'What's in it?' said the Queen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'I haven't opened it yet,' said the White Rabbit, 'but it seems to be a letter, written by the prisoner to-to somebody.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'It must have been that,' said the King, 'unless it was written to nobody, which isn't usual, you know.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'Who is it directed to?' said one of the jurymen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'No, they're not,' said the White Rabbit, 'and that's the queerest thing about it.' (The jury all looked puzzled.)",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'Please your Majesty,' said the Knave, 'I didn't write it, and they can't prove I did: there's no name signed at the end.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'If you didn't sign it,' said the King, 'that only makes the matter worse.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "You MUST have meant some mischief, or else you'd have signed your name like an honest man.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "There was a general clapping of hands at this: it was the first really clever thing the King had said that day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'That PROVES his guilt,' said the Queen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'It proves nothing of the sort!' said Alice. 'Why, you don't even know what they're about!'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'Read them,' said the King.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "The White Rabbit put on his spectacles.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'Where shall I begin, please your Majesty?' he asked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'Begin at the beginning,' the King said gravely, 'and go on till you come to the end: then stop.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "These were the verses the White Rabbit read:--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "'They told me you had been to her, And mentioned me to him: She gave me a good character, But said I could not swim.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "I gave her one, they gave him two, You gave us three or more; They all returned from him to you, Though they were mine before.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "If I or she should chance to be Involved in this affair, He trusts to you to set them free, Exactly as we were.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-168_123450_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/168/123450/168_123450_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "My notion was that you had been (Before she had this fit) An obstacle that came between Him, and ourselves, and it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
