        "content": "You fool! We'll pack up his dinner and send him to school. He shall learn about two times and parsing and capes, And how to make money with inches on tapes. We'll apprentice him then to the drapery trade, Where, I've heard it reported, large profits are made; Besides, he can sell us cheap buttons and braid.\"",
