        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-168",
        "content": "\"And now,\" said the teacher, \"the day's task brings Consideration of practical things. If a man makes a profit of fifteen pounds On one week's takings from two milk rounds, How many . . .\" And Sym went dreaming away To the sunlit lands where the field mice play, And wrens hold revel the livelong day.",
